{"tid":581411,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿仙奴或提早賣走藍斯 怕他夏天免費走人","createTime":"2018-03-05T10:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T18:08:30.000Z","uid":147522,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"9b694874571473713f4515ec9db7e11b751fc265","tid":581411,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:22:05.000Z","msg":"　　《每日郵報》消息，為了避免藍斯明年夏天免費走人，阿仙奴已準備出售他。<br />\n<br />\n　　<span style=\"color: red;\">藍斯的合約2019年夏天到期，阿仙奴高層擔心他會履行完合約，然後免費離隊。兵工廠已經在尋找接替者，為了避免奧斯爾和山齊士的鬧劇再次出現，他們今夏必須出售藍斯。</span><br />\n<br />\n　　山齊士在合約還剩半年時和米希達利恩互換東家，加盟曼聯，奧斯爾則和兵工廠簽下了一份週薪35萬英鎊的大合約。<br />\n<br />\n　　今季兵工廠再次陷入低谷，有可能連續兩年無緣歐聯，雲格和多名球員的未來都懸而未決。除了藍斯，威爾希爾目前也拒絕續約，他今夏就將成為自由人。<br />\n<br />\n星散啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fa4ba0d5ce1f22c6e7f7ae24c9c830ae5eaf1eb","tid":581411,"uid":19126,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾其實15萬都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英超首席隱形戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd399f984cab94f0501272a692340dbbef084d7d","tid":581411,"uid":36497,"like":4,"dislike":10,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:26:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>奧斯爾其實15萬都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n英超首席隱形戰機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n跑動咁多都隱形<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab4cc83996431698db22ab7ca411ba499aa3c365","tid":581411,"uid":372,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1fa4ba0d5ce1f22c6e7f7ae24c9c830ae5eaf1eb","tid":581411,"uid":19126,"like":27,"dislike":3,"score":24,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:23:01.000Z","msg":"奧斯爾其實15萬都唔值<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/so